<font color="#FF0000">ANSWER TO MR. DELEVA, SORT OF</font><br>
<tt>Thu Sep 25 23:50:15 US/Eastern 1997
</tt><p>
I know that PTSD is no laughing matter, but I couldn't resist this, following up on Joeseph DeLeva's post.<br><br>
1. Carrying a protest sign that weighs more than 2 lbs. = 1 point. 1 point per pound after that up to 6. too &quot;heavy&quot; after that. (Even if he is my brother).<br>
2. Being allergic to the flowers you stick in the National Guard soldiers gun barrels. 2 points.<br>
3. Being stupid and wearing sandles, instead of running shoes, at a anti-war protest. 3 points.<br>
4. Going to a anti-war protest and coming home alone (and not getting laid). lose 12 points.<br>
5. Getting laid after a great anti war rally, and then finding out 3 days later that you have a &quot;medical problem&quot;. lose 4 points.<br>
6. Punching a cop.  6 points.<br>
7. The cop punching you back. lost 4 points.<br>
8 The cop busting you for assault on a peace (what a pun) officer. 3 points.<br>
9. Actually liking the smell of petullcholie (sp?) oil or insense.  2 points.<br>
10. Taking your stash to a anti-war rally.  lose 4 points.<br>
11. Finding someone else's stash who dropped it while running away from an anti-war protest? 25 points.<br>
12. Being the main speaker at a anti war rally.  10 points<br>
13. Being &quot;security&quot; at the rally and not being a Black Panther member.  4 points.<br>
14. Drinking the orange juice in the gallon jug that Tim Leary just handed you.  lose your frontal lobes and 55 points.<br>
15. Finding you old lady is at the protest with your best friend.  2 points.<br>
16. Finding your old lady in the sack after the rally with your best friend and 5 other dudes.  lose 4 points, but if you stay cool, gain 22 points.<br>
17. Stay up all night on speed to make the most bitchin' anti war poster, all in day glow neon, and 2 minutes before the peace march, realize you spelled Peace wrong.   lost 31 points.<br>
18. Score some great pot at the rally, come home and find your draft notice just came in the mail.  3 points.<br>
19. Use your draft notice to roll joints in.  55 points.<br>
20. Tell the doc's at the induction physical that you are a fag, and they say, Oh, thats ok, we have a gay batallion we will put you in.  lose your dignity and 66 points.<br>
21. Thinking the Hells Angels are on your side.  lose 5 points.<br>
22. Thinking all girls love long hair on men.  lose 4 points.<br>
23. zipping up your parka over your long beard (ouch) lose 20 points.<br>
24. Waking up with a stanger who is ugly, and she thinks the same of you.   5 points.<br>
25. Get tired of hearing quotes from Chairman Mao and break up a serious meeting by quoting the Furry Freak Brothers Comic Book characters.  79 points.<br><br>
I feel much better. I hope you do too.  God those were some days.  Truly better in the &quot;bush&quot; back home then the jungle, but then again, those blondes did get boring after a few hundred or so.....
<p><code>-- Turn on, tune in, drop out, write mom  (doc &quot;cool &amp; groovy&quot;) </code><p>


